             was indicted for <rs id="t18130714-73-off423" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18130714-73-off423" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18130714-73-off423" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18130714-73-cd424" type="crimeDate">22nd of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130714-73-off423 t18130714-73-cd424"></join>, a mare, value 5 l. a cart, value 3 l. a cart harness, value 10 s. three casks, value 1 l. an apron, value 6 d. and one peck of pease, value 10 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18130714-73-victim766" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Bates
                  <interp inst="t18130714-73-victim766" type="surname" value="Bates"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18130714-73-victim766" type="given" value="William"></interp>
