                     <interp inst="t18130714-73-person769" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was coming through Southampton-court; I saw the pursuit, and I stopped the prisoner at the posts.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18130714-73-person770">
                  THOMAS 
                  TAYLOR
               <interp inst="t18130714-73-person770" type="surname" value="TAYLOR"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18130714-73-person770" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18130714-73-person770" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a constable. I searched the prisoner. I found these skeleton keys about the prisoner, thirty-three skeleton keys and a small crow.</p>
               <p>Q. to Mrs. Miles. What is the value of these tea-spoons - A. They are worth a shilling a piece.</p>
               <p>The prisoner said nothing in his defence; called three witnesses, who gave him a good character.</p>
               <p>
